it.polimi.se2018.model.events

Class MoveDie

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2018.model.events.ViewMessage
      • it.polimi.se2018.model.events.MoveDie
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MoveDie
extends ViewMessage
    This class is used to encapsulate the data needed to move an already placed Die on the Player's Pattern. This action is allowed by the 'Eglomise Brush' and 'Copper Foil Burnisher' ToolCard.
    Author:
    giorgiolabate
